==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Thirty years on the east side of the river, thirty years on the west side of the river.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: sān shí nían hé dōng, sān shí nían hé xī

===Phrase===
'''[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[东]]，[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[西]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Prosperity and decline never last.
# (''idiom'') Life has its ups and downs.
# (''idiom'') Everything in life is cyclical.

===Alternate forms===
[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[東]]，[[三]][[十]][[年]][[河]][[西]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

